# Cache directory for verify_rendering_correctness.py captures.
#
# The Vulkan-side .npy interop dumps are 64 MB raw per buffer (per-env
# layout: 4096 envs * 64*64*4 bytes); too large for git. Regenerated on
# every run that doesn't have a matching cached stamp.
#
# The Newton 16-env RGB reference (newton_16env/capture_newton_16env_rgb.npy)
# is only 192 KB and is renderer-independent, so we DO commit it so the
# suite has a reference baseline on a fresh checkout.
#
# JSON summaries + stamp.json files are small and worth keeping in
# version control so behaviour deltas across machines / branches are
# tracked.
vulkan_*/capture_*.npy
vulkan_*/*.ppm

